negotiator.config

Interface MultilateralTournamentConfigurationInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MultilateralTournamentConfiguration

    public interface MultilateralTournamentConfigurationInterface
    Stores the configuration variables

    This object must be serializable so that the configuration can be read from file. Therefore should not contain complex runtime objects but rather RepItems. Implementations should be immutable.
